---
title: 查看/調整配置
description: 配置健康度展示 + 6 項快速調整
links:
  - setup-main: 返回主流程
  - gmail-setup: Gmail 分級設定
---
flowchart TD
    Entry([從主流程進入]) --> Health[顯示配置健康度]

    Health --> Details["完整展開：
    Claude commands/agents/rules/hooks/settings
    CLAUDE.md repo 數量
    zsh 模組安裝狀態
    Slack 模式及頻道
    Gmail Script ID
    AI 模型設定"]

    Details --> Select{選擇調整項目}

    Select -->|Claude 配置| Claude[adjustClaude]
    Claude --> B1[備份 commands/agents/rules]
    B1 --> I1[handleInstallClaude 重新選擇安裝]
    I1 --> Done([調整完成])

    Select -->|全局設定| Settings[adjustGlobalSettings]
    Settings --> S1[deploySettings smart merge]
    S1 --> Done

    Select -->|CLAUDE.md| ClaudeMd[adjustClaudeMd]
    ClaudeMd --> CM1{session 有 repos?}
    CM1 -->|No| CMWarn[提示重新 setup]
    CM1 -->|Yes| CM2[AI 確認？]
    CM2 -->|Yes| CM3[generateClaudeMd × N repos]
    CM3 --> CM4[deployAllProjectClaudeMd]
    CM4 --> Done
    CM2 -->|No| Done

    Select -->|zsh 模組| Zsh[adjustZsh]
    Zsh --> Z1[備份 ~/.zsh/modules]
    Z1 --> Z2[handleInstallModules 重新選擇]
    Z2 --> Done

    Select -->|Slack 通知| Slack[adjustSlack]
    Slack --> SK1[setupSlackNotify 互動設定]
    SK1 --> Done

    Select -->|Gmail 分級| Gmail[adjustGmail]
    Gmail --> G1["setupGmailFilters 互動設定 →"]
    G1 --> Done

    Select -->|← 返回| Exit([已取消])
